window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The competition between Scions continues, with more on the line than ever before.</p> <p>Roy and his teammates have long odds to beat, especially seeing as they're up against the most powerful team in the entire tournament. With little hope of success, Roy will need to push himself as never before, discovering new depths to both his physical and spiritual power.</p> <p>All the while, Azure watches from on high as ancient seals continue to crumble, heralding the rise of a new age...</p>"; 
